
IMPORTANT KEYBOARD KEYS ON THE R65 SYSTEM

CT-q            clear to end of screen
CT-l            split/full screen graphics
CT-r            print all on
CT-t            print all off
(SH)CT-right    insert char
(SH)CT-left     delete char
(SH)CT-down     scroll down
(SH)CT-up       scroll up

  (SH)CT is required on Mac/UTM/Debian
